desc.value: There's a ton going on here.
She's a Maine Coon, and very elegant and pretty.
It looks like some weird antique your grandmother would have. Why would anyone carry this thing around?
It's immense, with rocky outcroppings. It looks very climbable.
Everything is very colorful, because everything has got paint on it.
It's barely wide enough to walk two by two down. The narrow walls really funnel the wind, creating powerful gusts.
It's dark, the cavern that is.
Whoa, how'd you even find this!?
